The look of the future has preoccupied philosophers and designers for
centuries. One company in Belgium, Living Tomorrow, is trying to make the
future more tangible by bringing together innovative product designers and
high-tech companies. The result is the House of the Future, which shows how
life could be more comfortable, and more energy efficient, sometime in the
future. Nina-Maria Potts reports.
 
 
 
 
 
 
